{"tid":1072396,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉偏袒舊老闆波音詆毀F-35 美國代理防長被調查","createTime":"2019-03-22T03:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T23:37:28.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"51c79c0851b3880905682058ad192a7a7b1b4222","tid":1072396,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:58:35.000Z","msg":"受到波音737 MAX客機事故影響，曾任該公司高層的美國代理防長夏納翰也成為外界檢視的焦點。五角大廈督察長辦公室20日證實，正針對夏納翰涉嫌以職權偏袒波音公司一案進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n稱波音F-15X比洛馬F-35「好很多」<br />\n<br />\n《英國廣播公司》（BBC）報導，五角大廈監察單位上週接獲華府「公民道德責任組織」投訴，援引媒體報導指出夏納翰在力推波音F-15X戰機的同時，「不忘」洛克希德馬丁研製的F-35戰機。報導指出，夏納翰聲稱「波音若拿下合約，表現絕對會比洛馬好很多」，明顯有偏袒老東家之意。<br />\n<br />\n提出控訴的團體指稱，夏納翰「可能違反相關操守規定」，五角大廈督察長辦公室發言人艾倫則表示，已告知夏納翰對其啟動調查程序。夏納翰對調查表示歡迎，期望「藉此釐清外界疑慮」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國代理防長夏納翰遭指控偏袒老東家。圖為由波音生產的美國空軍現役F-15E戰機。（取自DVIDS網站<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vasuqWVSLgL8ErxmF.7qlQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM3Ni44NzM2NjE2NzAyMzU1NQ--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/fLHm44qgMfPJKnRQEg5sPg--~B/aD01NTA7dz05MzQ7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/youthdailynews_517/650df4c39f7f18faebd19045e7089b6b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FvasuqWVSLgL8ErxmF.7qlQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM3Ni44NzM2NjE2NzAyMzU1NQ--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FfLHm44qgMfPJKnRQEg5sPg--~B%2FaD01NTA7dz05MzQ7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fyouthdailynews_517%2F650df4c39f7f18faebd19045e7089b6b&h=b07a8e6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/涉偏袒老東家波音-美代理防長被調查-160000119.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E6%B6%89%E5%81%8F%E8%A2%92%E8%80%81%E6%9D%B1%E5%AE%B6%E6%B3%A2%E9%9F%B3-%E7%BE%8E%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E9%98%B2%E9%95%B7%E8%A2%AB%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-160000119.html&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE6ha%2BoeUeRXR1jLQ0PybHu0%3D&h=4b0f360d\" target=\"_blan